Since the sentiment around TSLA seems negative, I have sold all 10 shares of TSLA at the current price, which has added approximately $4273.70 to our cash balance.

Our updated cash balance is now $4929.64, and we no longer hold any TSLA shares. We will continue to monitor the market and look for opportunities to invest in stocks that show signs of weakness, in line with our new strategy.
